        <CaseBranch><Str>'A'</Str><RW>..</RW><Str>'Z'</Str><RW>:</RW> <Assignment><SymbRef>x</SymbRef> <RW>:=</RW> <Num>2</Num></Assignment></CaseBranch><RW>;</RW>
    <RW>end</RW></Case><RW>;</RW>

    <Case><RW>case</RW> <SymbRef>kind</SymbRef> <RW>of</RW>
        <CaseBranch><Ident>red</Ident><RW>:</RW> <Assignment><SymbRef>ch</SymbRef> <RW>:=</RW> <Str>'r'</Str></Assignment></CaseBranch><RW>;</RW>
        <CaseBranch><Ident>green</Ident><RW>,</RW> <Ident>blue</Ident><RW>:</RW> <Assignment><SymbRef>ch</SymbRef> <RW>:=</RW> <Str>'g'</Str></Assignment></CaseBranch><RW>;</RW>
    <RW>end</RW></Case><RW>;</RW>
<RW>end</RW></Block><RW>.</RW></ProgramFile>
